ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 246, Saskatchewan
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER No. 246 in order to (1) declare the natural disaster to be of federal concern; and (2) authorize the provision of financial assistance to SASKATCHEWAN with respect to the wildfires that occurred from May 17, 2021 to October 20, 2021.
